Use nohup to run program in the background
    $ nohup sh sample.sh

or Close the terminal witghout terminating background process
    $ sh sample.sh
    $ press ctrl+z
    $ bg
    $ disown

    https://askubuntu.com/questions/757336/close-the-terminal-without-terminating-the-process


